Package com.cafean.client.ui.navigator

Class BeanArrayNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      • com.cafean.client.ui.navigator.NavigatorNode
        • com.cafean.client.ui.navigator.BeanArrayNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentListener, java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode
    public class BeanArrayNode
extends NavigatorNode
implements ComponentListener
    The BeanArrayNode allows the navigator to explore arrays of Beans that are contained inside other BeanNodes. Every child of a BeanArrayNode is a BeanNode. The BeanArrayNode allows the user to create new entries in the array.
